《'''QWOP'''》是一款於2008年推出的[[布娃娃系统|布娃娃系统]][[网页游戏|Flash游戏]]，由[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]樂隊{{tsl|en|Cut Copy}}前[[貝斯手|貝斯手]]貝內特·福迪（Bennett Foddy）開發。在遊戲中，玩家需要使用[[電腦鍵盤|鍵盤]]上的Q、W、O、P按鈕來控制一位名為「Qwop」的運動員。此遊戲於2010年12月[[網絡爆紅|網絡爆紅]]，並讓福迪的網站「Foddy.net」累積超過3000萬人次的瀏覽次數。<ref name="no-pain-no-gain">{{cite web|last=Benenson|first=Fred|url=http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2011/09/start/no-pain-no-gain|title=Meet Bennett Foddy: The man behind QWOP and GIRP|publisher=Wired Magazine|date=2011-08-02|accessdate=2011-08-14|archive-date=2011-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111006183641/http://www.wired.co.uk/magazine/archive/2011/09/start/no-pain-no-gain|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==背景==
[[File:Bennett_Foddy.jpg|thumb]]
《QWOP》是於2008年11月由貝內特·福迪為其網站「Foddy.net」創作。<ref name="QWOP info" />當時，福迪是[[牛津大學|牛津大學]][[牛津大學馬丁學院|馬丁學院]]新生物科學倫理計劃的副主任及高級研究員。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.neuroethics.ox.ac.uk/our_members/bennett_foddy | title=Bennett Foddy | publisher=The Oxford Centre for Neuroethics | accessdate=2012-03-13 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120327015044/http://www.neuroethics.ox.ac.uk/our_members/bennett_foddy | archivedate=2012-03-27 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.bep.ox.ac.uk/our_people/bennett_foddy | title=Dr Bennett Foddy | publisher=Insititue for Science and Ethics | accessdate=2012-03-13 | deadurl=yes | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927042903/http://www.bep.ox.ac.uk/our_people/bennett_foddy | archivedate=2012-09-27 }}</ref>在拖延[[哲學|哲學]][[論文|論文]]寫作的時候，貝內特自學了遊戲製作。<ref name="Gamasutra">{{cite web|last=Rose|first=Mike|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/40166/Road_to_the_IGF_Bennett_Foddys_GIRP.php|title=Road to the IGF: Bennett Foddy's GIRP|publisher=Gamasutra|date=2012-02-13|accessdate=2012-02-19|archive-date=2012-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120214065714/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/40166/Road_to_the_IGF_Bennett_Foddys_GIRP.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>自從他在5歲時得到了第一台電腦（[[Sinclair_ZX_Spectrum|ZX Spectrum]]）後，他便不停地玩電子遊戲。<ref name="Gamasutra" />因此，他對電子遊戲情有獨鍾。<ref>{{cite web|last=Brown|first=Mark|url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/news/2011/03/games-work-neurological-magic-says-qwop-creator.ars?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=rss&comments=1#comments-bar|title=Games work "neurological magic," says QWOP creator|date=March 2011|work=[[Wired_Magazine|Wired Magazine]]|publisher=[[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]|accessdate=2012-02-21}}</ref>

==遊戲系統==
在遊戲中，玩家需要控制一位名為「Qwop」的運動員完成[[奥林匹克运动会|奥林匹克运动会]]的[[100米賽跑|100米競跑賽事]]。透過使用[[電腦鍵盤|鍵盤]]上的Q、W、O、P按鈕，玩家需要控制Qwop腿的運動令他向前走动（Q、W控制左右大腿，而O、P控制小腿）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiegames.com/blog/2008/11/browser_game_pick_qwop_olympic.html|title=Browser Game Pick: QWOP (Benzido)|date=2008-11-07|accessdate=2010-12-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101211101406/http://www.indiegames.com/blog/2008/11/browser_game_pick_qwop_olympic.html|archive-date=2010-12-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

==反響==
玩家在此遊戲中的目標很簡單，就是控制Qwop向前走100米。但是，此遊戲的操控实则非常困難，致使不少玩家均無法完成遊戲。<ref name="What's so hard about QWOP?">{{cite news | url=http://www.manilastandardtoday.com/insideLifestyle.htm?f=2010/december/14/lifestyle2.isx&d=2010/december/14 | title=What’s so hard about QWOP? | accessdate=2010-12-25 | author=Biado, Ed | date=2010-12-14 | publisher=[[Manila_Standard_Today|Manila Standard Today]]}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first=Baby|last=Prokrastination|url=http://www.zeitjung.de/medien/medien/7296-internet-du-ort-ohne-langeweile-prokrastination-baby-qwop-shift-fmylifecom-badassbossde/|title=Internet, du Ort ohne Langeweile|publisher=Zeltijung|date=2012-02-08|accessdate=2012-02-19|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120211091423/http://www.zeitjung.de/medien/medien/7296-internet-du-ort-ohne-langeweile-prokrastination-baby-qwop-shift-fmylifecom-badassbossde/|archivedate=2012-02-11}}</ref>福迪亦指出他曾因此收到很多投訴信。<ref name="QWOPoficialinfo">Foddy, Bennett (December 2010). [http://www.foddy.net/?p=74 QWOP] {{Wayback|url=http://www.foddy.net/?p=74 |date=20161117030650 }}. foddy.net. Accessed from June 16, 2013.</ref>儘管此遊戲因操控困難而被批評<ref name="What's so hard about QWOP?" />，但此遊戲自從發佈後便累積了過百萬的玩家數量<ref>{{cite web|last=Salgado|first=Filipe|url=http://www.popsci.com/technology/article/2012-01/popsci-arcade|title=The PopSci Flash Arcade|publisher=[[PopSci|PopSci]]|date=2012-02-06|accessdate=2012-02-19|archive-date=2012-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120211200537/http://www.popsci.com/technology/article/2012-01/popsci-arcade|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並令福迪網站的瀏覽次數急升至3000萬人次。<ref name="no-pain-no-gain"/>

==突破與流行文化==
[[File:QWOP_Featured_in_2011.jpg|thumb]]
2010年12月初，此遊戲因為[[雷·威廉·約翰遜|雷·威廉·約翰遜]]在[[Youtube|Youtube]]上的推廣<ref name="The Most Difficult Game Ever Created Gameplay and Commentary">{{cite web|last=Cr1TiKaL (penguinz0)|title=The Most Difficult Game Ever Created Gameplay and Commentary|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EmcMG4uxiHk|work=Cr1TiKaL's Channel|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|accessdate=2010-12-28|archive-date=2010-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101218035531/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=EmcMG4uxiHk|dead-url=no}}</ref>而開始獲得知名度。<ref name="GOOFY RUN">{{cite web|last=Johnson|first=Ray William|title=GOOFY RUN|url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0i2zaDSXhFM|work=<nowiki>=3: RayWilliamJohnson's Channel</nowiki>|publisher=[[YouTube|YouTube]]|accessdate=2010-12-28|archive-date=2011-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110104000024/http://www.youtube.com//watch?v=0i2zaDSXhFM|dead-url=no}}</ref>此遊戲之後便逐漸成為了一個[[網絡迷因|網絡迷因]]。<ref name="Web Search Interest: qwop">{{cite web|url=http://www.google.com/insights/search/#q=qwop&date=today%201-m&cmpt=q|title=Web Search Interest: qwop|work=Google Insights for Search|publisher=[[Google|Google]]|accessdate=2010-12-25|archive-date=2012-09-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927083031/http://www.google.com/insights/search/#q=qwop&date=today%201-m&cmpt=q|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Independent">{{cite news | url=http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/current-google-insights-trends-elizabeth-edwards-qwop-and-chrome-os-2159209.html | title=Current Google Insights trends: Elizabeth Edwards, QWOP and Chrome OS | accessdate=2010-12-25 | publisher=[[The_Independent|The Independent]] | location=London | date=2010-12-13 | archive-date=2010-12-17 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101217044957/http://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/gadgets-and-tech/current-google-insights-trends-elizabeth-edwards-qwop-and-chrome-os-2159209.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>

2011年7月27日，此遊戲在[[紐約市|紐約市]][[現代藝術博物館|現代藝術博物館]]中展出。<ref name="Kill Screen Hosts Game Night at the Museum">{{cite news|last=Chai|first=Barbara|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/07/28/moma-hosts-kill-screen-arcade-where-everybody-can-play/|title=Kill Screen Hosts Game Night at the Museum|publisher=[[The_Wall_Street_Journal|The Wall Street Journal]]|accessdate=2011-08-15|date=2011-07-28|archive-date=2011-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110926000247/http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2011/07/28/moma-hosts-kill-screen-arcade-where-everybody-can-play/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

[[吉尼斯世界紀錄大全|吉尼斯世界紀錄大全]]後來更為此遊戲設定了一個世界紀錄，即「最快完成QWOP 100米賽跑的人」。2013年3月18日，[[奇恩塔马尼|奇恩塔马尼]]的拉瑪昌德拉·羅斯漢刷新了完成QWOP 100米賽跑的最快紀錄：1分零3秒（該年4月更是刷新為51秒）。<ref>[http://challengers.guinnessworldrecords.com/challenges/160-fastest-100m-run-qwop-flash-game Fastest 100m run, QWOP (flash game)] {{Wayback|url=http://challengers.guinnessworldrecords.com/challenges/160-fastest-100m-run-qwop-flash-game |date=20130315155736 }}. challengers.guinnessworldrecords.com. Accessed from March 28, 2013.</ref>

此遊戲亦曾於[[電視節目|電視連續劇]][[辦公室_(美國電視劇)|辦公室]]第9季中出現。<ref name="rantgaming">Johnson, Ryan. (September 24, 2012). [https://web.archive.org/web/20120926181259/http://www.rantgaming.com/2012/09/24/the-qwop-game-appears-on-the-office-premiere/ Indie Feature:The QWOP Game Makes an Appearance in The Office Season 9 Premiere]. rantgaming.com. Archived from September 26, 2012. Accessed from July 18, 2013.</ref>

